description: A TypeScript module exporting an Icon object containing SVG icon components as string-returning functions.

methods.name: Icon.Plus
methods.description: Returns SVG markup string for a plus icon.

methods.name: Icon.Edit
methods.description: Returns SVG markup string for an edit (pencil) icon.

methods.name: Icon.Delete
methods.description: Returns SVG markup string for a delete/trash icon.

methods.name: Icon.Save
methods.description: Returns SVG markup string for a save icon.
